(20, 1, '2022-12-30 08:23:54', '2022-12-30 08:23:54', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Laima Unisex Hair &amp; Beauty salon provides a wide range of services. Our qualified and highly skilled team help you create the perfect style, to emphasise your natural beauty and personality. Great location, unique design, advanced equipment, an individual approach to each client and a friendly atmosphere sets us apart from other salons. We employ only highly qualified professionals, creative and dedicated people. Good quality and affordable prices will not leave you unsatisfied. We always follow the latest developments in the world of beauty, are interested in fashion trends and constantly try to improve our services. If you’re looking for a great new hair cut or colour, hair extensions, classic and modern gents cuts, come and see us at Laima Unisex Hair &amp; Beauty. We also offer a wide range of high quality beauty treatments for the face and body. These include facials, eyelashes and eyebrows care, body massages and wraps, hot and warm waxing, mesotherapy etc. Nail services are among our most popular services, which is why we offer long-lasting manicures and pedicures from Gelish, CND Shellac, GelColor by OPI.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:uagb/buttons {\"block_id\":\"acd9165e\",\"classMigrate\":true,\"childMigrate\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-buttons uagb-buttons__outer-wrap uagb-btn__default-btn uagb-btn-tablet__default-btn uagb-btn-mobile__default-btn uagb-block-acd9165e\"><div class=\"uagb-buttons__wrap uagb-buttons-layout-wrap\"><!-- wp:uagb/buttons-child {\"block_id\":\"3a9d366f\",\"label\":\"Book Now\",\"link\":\"https://tinyurl.com/y3je5hnn\",\"color\":\"#ffffff\",\"background\":\"var(\\u002d\\u002dast-global-color-0)\",\"opensInNewTab\":true,\"boxShadowVOffset\":18,\"boxShadowBlur\":40,\"boxShadowSpread\":-10,\"btnBorderTopWidth\":1,\"btnBorderLeftWidth\":1,\"btnBorderRightWidth\":1,\"btnBorderBottomWidth\":1,\"btnBorderTopLeftRadius\":30,\"btnBorderT