(205, 1, '2023-01-01 06:01:44', '2023-01-01 06:01:44', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Amidst the daily hustle-bustle of life, the one thing that we often put on the back burner is the hair care routine. It’s not a good practice. A hair care routine for women is as essential as a&nbsp;skincare routine. It is not only about using your regular shampoo and conditioner but a lot more.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:uagb/advanced-heading {\"block_id\":\"cf1c5f07\",\"classMigrate\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-cf1c5f07\"><h2 class=\"uagb-heading-text\">1.&nbsp;<strong>Use the right shampoo:</strong></h2></div>\n<!-- /wp:uagb/advanced-heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The first thing in your hair care routine for women is to wash your hair properly. Make sure to choose the right shampoo whenever you need to cleanse your scalp and hair. It would be great if you find a natural one free from toxic chemicals and artificial fragrances. Also, when you buy shampoo for your hair, find one as per your specific hair type. Since every hair type is different from another, you need a shampoo that’s solely meant for you. It will help cleanse, nourish and strengthen your hair follicles in the best way possible.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:uagb/advanced-heading {\"block_id\":\"29a321e5\",\"classMigrate\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-29a321e5\"><h2 class=\"uagb-heading-text\">2.&nbsp;<strong>Don’t shampoo daily:</strong></h2></div>\n<!-- /wp:uagb/advanced-heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You might think your hair needs a vigorous session of hair cleansing due to extreme dirt, sweat, stress and pollution around you. But you would be happy to know that despite this stress-filled and polluted scenario, your hair does not require the daily dose of shampoo. Too much shampooing can steal the natural moisture of your hair, resulting in dry, damaged and frizzy hair. To prevent it happen to your hair, limit shampooing your hair twice a week.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:uagb/advanced-heading {\"block_id\":\"f1dfeca8\",\"classMigrate\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-f1dfeca8\"><h2 class=\"uagb-heading-text\">3.&nbsp;<strong>Follow up with conditioner:</strong></h2></div>\n<!-- /wp:uagb/advanced-heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Using the right shampoo for the hair care routine for women is good but it alone won’t make any difference. Thus, you need to use the right conditioner in combination with your shampoo. Using the right conditioner as per your hair type will help nourish your scalp, leaving your hair feeling soft, shiny, healthy and moisturized.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:uagb/advanced-heading {\"block_id\":\"60443be8\",\"classMigrate\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-60443be8\"><h2 class=\"uagb-heading-text\">4.&nbsp;<strong>Trim regularly:</strong></h2></div>\n<!-- /wp:uagb/advanced-heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Having long hair is good but skipping trimming is a big no for the hair care routine. Getting your hair regularly trimmed is essential to maintaining good hair health. So, choose a suitable hairstyle and make sure to trim your hair accordingly after every month without fail.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:uagb/advanced-heading {\"block_id\":\"d6f07103\",\"classMigrate\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-d6f07103\"><h2 class=\"uagb-heading-text\">5.&nbsp;<strong>Treat your hair gently:</strong></h2></div>\n<!-- /wp:uagb/advanced-heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Get your hair game on by treating it gently with love and care. Don’t rub, pull or comb your wet hair; it will promote hair damage and breakage. Also, it can lead to hair thinning, which in turn will damage your scalp.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '5 steps to follow for a complete hair care routine for women', 'Amidst the daily hustle-bustle of life, the one thing that we often put on the back burner is the hair care routine. It’s not a good practice. A hair care routine for women is as essential as a skincare routine. It is not only about using your regular shampoo and conditioner but a lot more. ', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '197-autosave-v1', '', '', '2023-01-01 06:01:44', '2023-01-01 06:01:44', '', 197, 'http://localhost/my_wp/?p=205', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(206, 1, '2023-01-01 06:04:09', '2023-01-01 06:04:09', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Laima Unisex Hair &amp; Beauty salon provides a wide range of services. Our qualified and highly skilled team help you create the perfect style, to emphasise your natural beauty and personality. Great location, unique design, advanced equipment, an individual approach to each client and a friendly atmosphere sets us apart from other salons. We employ only highly qualified professionals, creative and dedicated people. Good quality and affordable prices will not leave you unsatisfied. We always follow the latest developments in the world of beauty, are interested in fashion trends and constantly try to improve our services. If you’re looking for a great new hair cut or colour, hair extensions, classic and modern gents cuts, come and see us at Laima Unisex Hair &amp; Beauty. We also offer a wide range of high quality beauty treatments for the face and body. These include facials, eyelashes and eyebrows care, body massages and wraps, hot and warm waxing, mesotherapy etc. Nail services are among our most popular services, which is why we offer long-lasting manicures and pedicures from Gelish, CND Shellac, GelColor by OPI.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:uagb/buttons {\"block_id\":\"207c822a\",\"classMigrate\":true,\"childMigrate\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-buttons uagb-buttons__outer-wrap uagb-btn__default-btn uagb-btn-tablet__default-btn uagb-btn-mobile__default-btn uagb-block-207c822a\"><div class=\"uagb-buttons__wrap uagb-buttons-layout-wrap\"><!-- wp:uagb/buttons-child {\"block_id\":\"6d4c154b\",\"label\":\"Book Now\",\"link\":\"https://tinyurl.com/y3je5hnn\",\"color\":\"#ffffff\",\"background\":\"var(\\u002d\\u002dast-global-color-0)\",\"opensInNewTab\":true,\"boxShadowVOffset\":18,\"boxShadowBlur\":40,\"boxShadowSpread\":-10,\"btnBorderTopWidth\":1,\"btnBorderLeftWidth\":1,\"btnBorderRightWidth\":1,\"btnBorderBottomWidth\":1,\"btnBorderTopLeftRadius\":30,\"btnBorder